>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Soloing The Grey questions</span><hr size=1> I was wondering if it is possible soloing in The Grey for a non-epic 57th Mage?  If so, anybody have any tips on where to set up camp, what mobs drop some of the nicer loot, where they can be found, etc. etc. <br>
<br>
<br>
Sobbie ~~<br>
57th Gnomish Mage<br>
